    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ 425°F/ Gas 7</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced red onion</strong> to a bowl, cover with <strong>boiled water </strong>and set aside for later</p>",
