    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es] </span></strong>finely</p><p>Chop the <strong>cucumber<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>finely</p><p>Chop the <strong>parsley </strong>roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Add everything to a bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>Israeli-style chopped salad</strong></p>",
